ansible			:	Main command to invoke ansible
ansible-config		:	initialize or deal with ansible configuration
ansible-console		:	Run commands on all the hosts at-a-time
ansible-doc		:	Documentation for all ansible commands
ansible-galaxy		:	Initialize and use ansible roles and other features
ansible-inventory	:	Manage all types of hosts even dynamic inventory
ansible-playbook	:	Operate ansible-playbook
ansible-pull		:	Pull playbooks from a remote repo and play on tartget hosts
ansible-vault		: 	Encryption/Decryption utility for ansible datafiles
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- To know TOTAL NUMBER OF HOSTS that are associated with any host file

ansible-inventory all -i hosts --graph (or)
ansible all -i hosts --list-hosts


